  <brief_title>R-CHOP Versus R-mini-CEOP in Elderly Patients(&gt;65)With DLBCL</brief_title>
  <acronym>ANZINTER3</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized Phase III Randomized Study to Compare R-CHOP Versus R-mini-CEOP in Elderly Patients (&gt;65 Years) With Diffuse Large B Cell Lymphoma (DLBCL)</official_title>
