  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study has the purpose to compare R-CHOP versus R-mini-CEOP in elderly patients (&gt;65
      years) with Diffuse Large B Cell Lymphoma (DLBCL).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
